{"tid":86712,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[Old news] 徐佳瑩首新歌《是日救星》好正","createTime":"2017-01-19T09:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T10:19:15.000Z","uid":4260,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4940155126128389a0b31c39e823c4c7efcd2d54","tid":86712,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:29:24.000Z","msg":"Mv: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/EjRLwXByuRg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEjRLwXByuRg&d=lLDkewc10%2F2bRfwr4nLAHHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=aa0bd19b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EjRLwXByuRg</a><br />\n<br />\n編曲好華麗，好鍾意入面既民謠結他聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好鍾意第四段「請留意你快失控的正面思考 沒有什麼大不了 卻也小不了」，la la既咬字好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成首歌簡直係高潮迭起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e13a7cd7d3aa500149844e1977b8349cd6f6b8e4","tid":86712,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:31:38.000Z","msg":"曲：鄭楠、徐佳瑩 詞:徐佳瑩<br />\n<br />\n請注意你快著魔的正義嗜好<br />\n我收斂我快長繭的感動細胞<br />\n事情會 好解決一些<br />\n<br />\n別再浪費版面做平衡報導<br />\n我也懶得演解語花那一套<br />\n說真的 太入戲 很傷胃<br />\n<br />\n你本來就不在 要證明什麼存在<br />\n今天爆炸前快救自己出來<br />\n大家都狀況外 是笨蛋也是心肝<br />\n全買單你做得到嗎？<br />\n<br />\n請留意你快失控的正面思考<br />\n沒有什麼大不了 卻也小不了<br />\n已接種 負能量疫苗<br />\n<br />\n最完美的是我們一樣無聊<br />\n最要命的是只有你才救得了<br />\n快出手 越荒謬越好<br />\n<br />\n你本來就不在 要證明什麼存在<br />\n今天爆炸前快救自己出來<br />\n大家都狀況外 一頭熱喚醒冷感<br />\n這就是你要的嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我其實也不乖 要證明什麼可愛<br />\n他們說說你就信 找我麻煩<br />\n誰愛我的搞怪 愛我懶散的姿態<br />\n全買單你做得到嗎？ <br />\n再說吧！<br />\n<br />\n睇返YouTube至知係陳君豪編曲，開頭以為係鄭楠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a82330f319d8809a1899ce099deb5c5cafd1c4b","tid":86712,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T03:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082e6a3d3b94f05cec96cf4c71e2a2a3c663b5c6","tid":86712,"uid":36750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:08:46.000Z","msg":"後半段爆發嗰下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ff14956accfc7be7d07773f556e53a748cbd4c","tid":86712,"uid":218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:12:38.000Z","msg":"LaLa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4246639458757fb44a2cac8b47a2af54f9c73ce2","tid":86712,"uid":6132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:34:34.000Z","msg":"徐佳瑩6月個紅館演唱會幾時有得買飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02cccb27e8eee43e58eea3a64d210091c7a0f7c5","tid":86712,"uid":23360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T03:12:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>徐佳瑩6月個紅館演唱會幾時有得買飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b12478e39e98232929601a6438a9d57bdce11c","tid":86712,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T09:39:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>徐佳瑩6月個紅館演唱會幾時有得買飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n3月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322a3d4c35243cbb978b4a26a2010a350f316eb0","tid":86712,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T09:40:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>後半段爆發嗰下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等6月聽live<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLa la曲詞都好有水準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class